title: Berkley doubles up in state championships, video
text:
Berkley doubles up in state champions... Berkley doubles up in state championships, video Next Story Prev Story 5 hrs ago Read more: Bendigo Advertiser 
Bendigo's Berkley Wood has taken out first prize in the juvenile category of both the Victorian Open Dancesport Championships and the Tasmanian Open Dancesport Championship. The 11-year-old and her dance partner Sam Brown, 12, topped the field in the standard, new vogue and Latin American styles, tackling everything from waltz to foxtrot, samba to cha-cha.   Bendigo Advertiser.
